{"tid":693393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：Apple出片歌頌 香港「頭文字的」","createTime":"2018-06-07T12:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T12:28:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1398984350842b8e3469051e84ebe9dee103c7fd","tid":693393,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:17:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180607/20413361\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180607%2F20413361&d=49PVwSL8tEzP4Prf3PHnqWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=42bda8a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180607%2F20413361&h=1c5797b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180607/20413361</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月07日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：Apple出片歌頌<br />\n香港「頭文字的」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180607/large/a1103a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180607%2Flarge%2Fa1103a.gif&h=fe9e5e5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■3個Animoji問香港的士司機點解要揸咁快。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「細旗」（短程）唔做、機場嫌遠、過海唔識路，香港的士司機可以話係服務業界嘅打工皇帝，「優點」多多嘅香港的士司機，估唔到仲揚名海外，連國際數碼產品大品牌Apple都唱佢哋。Apple嘅YouTube頻道早兩日出咗條片，用Animoji效果整咗條MV，內容係咩呢？就係馳名中外嘅的士大哥喇！<br />\n<br />\n但首歌唔係講的士嘅拒載問題，而係講的士司機為咗走多幾轉，所以越揸越快，對香港人嚟講見怪不怪，但對外國人嚟講，每次上的士就要預備面對死亡咁，呢首歌正正唱出佢哋嘅心聲。<br />\n<br />\n歌詞提到香港的士司機點解咁匆忙，令到乘客如坐針氈，仲會問乘客旅行開唔開心？但其實作為遊客好驚，驚到縮埋一嚿。短片放上網短短兩日，點擊率已去到800萬，令到香港的士揚名海外。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：MK動作巨星　趴的士頂發爛渣<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片：斷纜爆火花　西環現電車龍"},{"pid":"b92915dffdd3da0224ba9ceb9a4a3e1accae3851","tid":693393,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:18:12.000Z","msg":"小巴司機表示笑而不語"},{"pid":"9c72873e74bb74f3d49a0ef917fefaf6d60a469c","tid":693393,"uid":37912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:28:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}